an overall air of confident swagger that their holder might also like to see in themselves. For CTJR, the art is not just
an image, but a reflection of an individual’s best self.

data.name: Crypto Alien Punk v1
data.description:
We are wasting time, energy, and resources trying to find the simplest single-cell creatures buried under icy Martian north pole glaciers, minuscule isopoda doing acrobatic stunts in spiralling Enceladus geyser jets, or primitive plants in the creases of Europa icy ground. In such an early stage of advancement in human’s evolution, we are so ignorant that we’ve never even tried to dig deeper than our own graves to find the true origin of humankind. Are we what we believe we are? Or are we just an ant farm abandoned a long time ago by a supreme being we call God?

Few people ask: are we alone in the universe? Or somewhere out there other intelligent beings or entities are looking up into their sky asking the same question? Are there civilisations more advanced than ours? Or are there civilisations that have achieved interstellar communication and have established a network of linked societies throughout our universe?

The answer is still beyond reach….

data.name: CryptoCrystal
data.description:
CryptoCrystal is a Japanese NFT gaming and collectibles project, released on May 11, 2018. The Shiny Crystals have personalities similar to humans while being overly cute like pet animals. Each of them is unique on Ethereum, with no duplicated DNA structure. Players can enjoy mining, collecting, and trading mysterious living minerals that live inside the Blockchain.

CryptoCrystal was created as a subproject of Quan Inc., a prominent digital character company based in Tokyo, Japan with over 4.5 billion global downloads. Eventually, the project was handed over to the original developer team, who went on to release a mobile game in Japan using the CryptoCrystal IP, with over 70,000 downloads so far.

Inspired by the success of Axie Infinity, CryptoCrystals is working to implement a play-to-earn model into their game. The vision is to allow players to collect the valuable Crystals in VR or in the meta-verse, similar to Pokemon GO.

data.name: CryptoFoxes
data.description:
CryptoFoxes are the only NFTs minted with a slot machine on the Ethereum blockchain. They are 11,111 for sale on [www.cryptofoxes.io](https://cryptofoxes.io/). They are the second generation of our collection. All the important details about the collection are on [www.cryptofoxes.io](https://cryptofoxes.io/).

All the assets are handcrafted, then the CryptoFoxes are generated with a Python script in 48x48 GIF and scaled to 480x480 and minted on a Smart Contract ERC721 on Ethereum Blockchain. Each one is unique and crafted with its properties. Some of them are super rare!

Follow our [Twitter](https://twitter.com/CryptoFoxesNFT) for the latest news and join our [Discord](https://discord.gg/3crJeNYssT) to chat with the community.

The Origin collection is [here](https://opensea.io/collection/cryptofoxes-origin-steak).
